  "title": "Clinic Assistant (4 days, Northeast) #HAC",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Scope:</strong></p><p>* Registering of patients under the right category of Private, CHAS, CDMP, MBS and Corporate patients</p><p>* Assist doctors in procedures, such as ECG, dressing procedures and medical examinations.</p><p>* Pack and dispense prescribed medication to patients.</p><p>* Collection of payment and/or process claims for CHAS, CDMP, MBS and Corporate patients.</p><p>* Arrange/Booking appointment for patients for follow-up treatment and vaccination.</p><p>* Daily e-submission of Managed Care claims for different insurance schemes</p><p>* Any other duties as may be assigned by Immediate Supervisor and/or the Management.<br /></p><p><strong>Requirements: </strong><br /><br />* Min O Levels and above<br />* Able to start immediately <br /></p><p><strong>Interested candidates please send your resume to anna.chen@recruitexpress.com.sg</strong><br /></p><p>Anna Chen jiaxin</p><p>CEI No: R25157621</p><p>Recruit Express Pte Ltd  </p><p>EA License: 99C4599</p>",
